    {
      "id": "identity-details",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 125,
      "y": 200,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 280,
      "text": "idm.lab.forge.local\n10.0.1.10\nOracle Linux 8\n\n--- Services ---\nFreeIPA (KDC + LDAP + DNS)\n  :88   Kerberos\n  :389  LDAP\n  :53   DNS\n  :443  Web UI\n\nKeycloak (Docker)\n  :9080 HTTP\n  :9443 HTTPS\n\nPostgreSQL (Docker)\n  :5433",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
