    {
      "id": "api-details",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 435,
      "y": 200,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 280,
      "text": "api.lab.forge.local\n10.0.1.11\nOracle Linux 8\n\n--- Services ---\nNginx (reverse proxy)\n  :443  HTTPS (TLS)\n  :80   HTTP redirect\n\n.NET Core 8 API\n  :5000 Kestrel (HTTP)\n\nSSSD (domain auth)\nKerberos keytab:\n  HTTP/api.lab.forge.local",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
